  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to identify that whether PD-1/PD-L1 pathway will change in human
      sepsis, and whether PD-1/PD-L1 pathway play an important role in sepsis induced
      immunosuppression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      First, we will detect PD-L1 expression on PBMC of septic patients and healthy controls.

      Second, blockade of PD-1/PD-L1 pathway in vitro and stimulate with some biomolecules and then
      analyze the PBMC function and apoptosis by flow cytometry.

      Then, compare with healthy controls and find the differences.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
